#   JS tickets: the JABC (JavaScriptCore) bindings

`js/` is JABC ‚Äî a thin, anti-bloat JavaScriptCore binding (stock
`libjavascriptcore`; bindings "hold no memory"; JS owns the buffers, no shared
custody). Tickets here cover exposing ABC primitives/containers to JS and the
binding surface. The fix-and-land method is [Issues].

